Pineapple ginger juice is a healthy drink. It is also sweet and delicious. Ingredients •Pineapple peeled and cut •Ginger •Lime • Water Instructions •In a blender, simply blend the pineapple and ginger with the water until all the ingredients are pureed. •Strain the juice into a clean container with a fine mesh strainer •Squeeze the lime juice into the juice, make sure you remove the seeds and then stir..Serve chilled. 